#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This behavior can be disabled by setting the `quarkus.elasticsearch.health.enabled` property to `false` in your `application.properties`."
msgstr "您可以在 `application.properties` 文件中将 `quarkus.elasticsearch.health.enabled` 属性设置为 `false` ，以禁用此行为。"

